\ the world and the name of Mr. Hobbs have been abused 

by the several spurious editions of the ' History of the Civil 

Wars,' wherein, by various and unskilful transcriptions, are 

committed above a thousand faults, and in above a hundred 

A^ places whole lines left out, as I can make appear. I must 

