but I find little in them of what I would ask. Therefore, 
since you were pleased to enter into this discourse at my 
request, be pleased also to inform me afler my own method ; 
and for the danger of confusion that may arise from that, I 
will take care to bring you back to the place from whence I 
drew you ; for I well remember where it was. 



