£. What a spiteful article was this! All the rest proceeded 
from ambition, which many times well-natured men are 
subject to; but this proceeded from an inhuman and devilish 
cruelty. 

A. 15. That the forts and castles be put under the com- 
mand of such persons as, with the approbation of the Par* 
