B. Methinks these very propositions sent to the King are 
an actual rebellion. 

A. 1 7. That his Majesty *be pleased to* enter into a more 
strict alliance with the United Provinces, and other neigh- 
bour Protestant Princes and States. 

18. That his Majesty be pleased, by act of Parliament, to 
